A stashed prefetch that overlaps the accepted stage but doesn't extend beyond it is cleared, not used. After accept the engine triggers a new prefetch and goes idle because the cursor target is close.
row: 2
col: 0
viewportTop: 1
viewportBottom: 20
-- buffer.txt --
function add(a, b) {

}
-- steps --
completion 2-2
  | "  return a + b;"
expect shown state=hasCompletion

stash-prefetch 2-2
  | "  return a + b;"

accept
expect state=idle prefetchState=waitingForCursorPrediction
  buffer:
    | "function add(a, b) {"
    | "  return a + b;"
    | "}"

